 results  sports sponsorship  references  external links historyedit southern kuzbass coal company acquired control over chelyabinsk steel plant in the summer of  and subsequently announced a merger of southern kuzbass and mechel into mechel steel group igor zyuzin was elected as chairman of the board of mechel steel group oao in january  mergers and acquisitionsedit mechel acquired posyet sea commercial port on the russian coast of the sea of japan in  mechel submitted a winning bid for a  stake in izhstal in may  subsequently increasing its stake to control mechel won an auction in january  to buy a blocking stake  plus one share of stock in yakutugol also in  mechel acquired a controlling stake in kambarka river port in october  mechel bought control in moscow coke and gas plant mechel acquired a controlling stake in southern kuzbass gres oao and kuzbassenergosbyt power sales company in  also in  mechel added to its asset portfolio the bratsk ferroalloy plant the largest producer of highsilicon content ferrosilicon in eastern siberia producing  metric tons of this material per annum or approximately  of the total russian ferrosilicon output in may  to assure a reliable inhouse source of raw materials mechel acquired a license to develop the uvat quartzite proven and probable reserves of this site are about  million metric tons but earlier estimates indicate that p proven probable and possible reserves of the deposit can be as high as  million tons in september  mechel acquired the mechel temryuk sea port on the taman peninsula in the sea of azov in october mechel won the auction to buy a controlling stake in yakutugol increasing its overall stake from  and one share to  mechel also acquired elga coal field mechel acquired oriel resources ltd in april  which controls the tikhvin ferroalloy plant in leningrad region the shevchenko nickel deposit in kazakhstan and the voskhod chromite deposit in kazakhstan the tikhvin plant has an annual projected capacity of  metric tons of ferroalloys mechel launched a new refinery mechel chrome at the voskhod deposit in september  with annual capacity of approximately  metric tons of chromite concentrate per annum mechel signed a deal to sell the tikhvin ferroalloy plant and the voskhod refinery to turkeys yildirim group in  the usmillion deal was closed in december  mechel negotiated the acquisition of  in us bluestone coal in  for an estimated us billion approximately however the price was revised downward in early  because of the great recession mechel was to pay for the asset us million and issue  of the postacquisition equity in preferred stock to the current shareholders of bluestone coal mechel trans a mechel logistics and transportation subsidiary acquired a controlling stake  in the vanino sea commercial port for rub  billion from the government at an auction in early december  only one month later mechel resold most of its recently acquired stake to a consortium of russian and international investors the company later acquired  of the ports common stock from en for rub billion mechel sold  of common stock in vanino port for rub  billion on october   retaining only  in the port  criticism from the governmentedit russian thenprime minister vladimir putin sharply criticized mechel management at a government meeting in nizhniy novgorod on july   which focused on ongoing troubles in the steel industry putin accused mechel for exporting raw materials for steelmakers at prices about half the domestic level which could be a sign of tax avoidance after putins accusations mechels stock dropped  on the new york stock exchange while the russian federal antimonopoly service launched investigation into mechels practice of raising domestic coking coal prices far above the export price levels on the following day july  the company issued a contrite statement promising full cooperation with federal authorities while share values rebounded by nearly  percent however vladimir putin once again criticized mechels management on july  during a government meeting on transfer pricing narrowing down his complaint “ when the domestic price is rub  per ton they sell the raw materials to themselves to their own offshore subsidiaries in this case to switzerland at rub  per ton which is only onequarter the domestic price  ” after this the stock price which had recovered a little over the previous days collapsed by another  producing a combined decline of  the companys market capitalization in august  was still half its value in july  in midaugust  the federal antimonopoly service found mechel guilty of violating article  of the competition law by causing the domestic price of coking to rise imposing a relatively small fine for this violation equivalent to  of the groups annual sales or rub  million in addition fas recommended that mechel should reduce the domestic price of coking coal by  this caused an additional weakness in the stock price in the wake of these events mechel announced on august  that a preferred share issue previously planned for placement on august  was to be postponed indefinitely this essentially closed the door to equity finance for mechel restricting its financing options to debt vladimir putin expressed regret over his own comments at a steel industry meeting in chelyabinsk on july   “ how can mechel organize normal decent fair business operation i remember my diatribe against mechel and i can only regret that it led to a more than  decline in the companys market capitalization i want to thank igor zyuzin — he did everything we spoke about and he has been on the best fair behavior ” conflicts with minority shareholdersedit mechel has had numerous conflicts with minority shareholders practically from the time of its incorporation minority shareholders have accused mechel of disregarding their rights vostok nafta prosperity capital metage capital and hq fonder accused mechel in — of unfairly reducing the buyout stock price during consolidation of mechels subsidiary southern kuzbass assets the federal service for financial markets confirmed that mechel had in fact violated minority shareholders rights by withholding essential information from them eventually mechel was forced to buy out the minority shareholders at the market price in  at the time when the russian environmental watchdog rosprirodnadzor filed claims against mechel subsidiaries a minority shareholder in tomusinsky open pit mine oao which is part of southern kuzbass the swiss bank julius baer and co ltd accused tomusinsky of issuing stock at a lower price in violation of the law and shareholders rights in  saven which held a  equity stake in tomusinsky open pit mine oao filed nine suits with an arbitration court claiming more than rub  billion from tomusinsky and several other subsidiaries of mechel yakutugol mechel mining mechel service mechel trans and mechel energo saven accused the defendants of diverting profits under the guise of lowinterest loans to companies affiliated with mechel on conditions clearly detrimental to themselves at interest rates ‘‘below’’ the russian central banks refinancing rate ie well below the market interest rate and without any collateral argasera also filed a suit in  against mechel subsidiary urals stampings plant oao courts have invariably ruled for the plaintiffs in these suits late  problemsedit mechel stock unexpectedly dropped sharply towards the end of  the stock dropped  on november   losing another  of their value the following day mechels market capitalization decreased from us  billion in may  to us  million in late  while the groups debt had mounted to us  billion the company started delaying wage payments and contractual payments to suppliers industry experts are unanimous that the companys trouble arise from inefficient acquisitions and highly risky financing policy which has practically brought mechel to the brink of bankruptcy the company has been forced to engage in tough negotiations with both russ