a of japan port posiet and on the sea of azov port temryuk and a freight river port on the kama river a tributary of the volga river in central russia port kambarka the company has a fleet of freight railcars locomotives and longhaul trucks and operates a rail line to its elga coal deposit in the sakha republicmining segmentthe mining segment produces metallurgical coal coking coal pulverized coal injection pci and anthracite steam coal iron ore concentrate coke and limestone the mining segment primarily consists of its coal iron ore and coke production facilities in russia the mining segment also includes limestone operations certain transportation and logistics facilities and engineering operations the companys subsidiary southern kuzbass coal company pao southern kuzbass coal company and its subsidiaries operate coal mines located in the kuznetsky basin near mezhdurechensk in western siberia these mines include approximately four open pit mines and over three underground minesthe companys subsidiary yakutugol jointstock holding company yakutugol operates coal mines located in the sakha republic in eastern siberia consisting of approximately two open pit mines and an underground mine yakutugol also holds subsoil licenses for over three iron ore deposits located near to its coal mining operations the mining segment also provides coal washing services to its coal mining subsidiaries korshunov mining plant oao operates approximately two open pit iron ore mines and a washing plant located near zheleznogorskilimsky a town in the irkutsk region in eastern siberia southern kuzbass coal company produces bituminous coal yakutugol produces hard coking coal of lowvolatile contentthe company offers coal tar naphthalene and other compounds the elga open pit is located in the southyakutsky basin of the toko coalbearing region in the sakha republic the company operates approximately six coal washing plants and a processing unit in russia which have an aggregate annual capacity of approximately  million tons of runofmine rom coal the companys coke plants are located in the city of chelyabinsk and in the moscow region the company also produces coke nut the pugachevsky limestone quarry is an open pit mine located approximately nine kilometers southwest of beloretsk in the ural mountainssteel segmentthe steel segment produces and sells semifinished steel products long products of a range of steel grades carbon and stainless flat steel products and valueadded metal products including wire products stampings and forgings the companys steel production facilities in russia include an integrated steel mill a steelmaking mill a wire products plant and forgings and stampings mill in the southern ural mountains and a wire products plant in northwestern russia near the border with finland the company also has a wire products plant in lithuania and a steel mill in ukrainethe company offers semifinished billets blooms and slabs the company offers its customers a range of long products produced from various steel grades including rebar calibrated long steel products steel angles round products surfaceconditioned steel products wire rod and others the companys wire products line includes spring wire rope wire bearing wire microwire precision alloy wire high and low carbon concrete reinforcing wire galvanized wire coppercoated and bright welding wire strand of various application various types of nails steel wire ropes specially engineered for the shipping aerospace oil and gas and construction industries steel wire ropes for passenger and freight elevators generalpurpose wire steel straps and clips chain link fences welded reinforcing meshes and otherspower segmentthe power segment includes the operations of southern kuzbass power plant oao southern kuzbass power plant located in kaltan in the kemerovo region the power segment sells electricity and capacity to the wholesale market as well as supplies electricity within the company the company also holds interests in kuzbass power sales company oao a power distribution company in the kemerovo region the southern kuzbass power plant has an installed capacity of approximately  megawatts and installed heat capacity of over  gigacalories per hourthe company competes with novolipetsk steel pao magnitogorsk iron  steel works oao severstal pao evraz plc metalloinvest holding company ao kuznetsk ferroalloys oao chelyabinsk electrometallurgical plant oao sibuglemet holding ummc suek ao stroyservis zao sds holding company en group russian coal oao kuzbasskaya toplivnaya company pao and zarechnaya coal company » full overview of mtl company address mechel pao ulkrasnoarmeyskaya dmoscow      p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation igor zyuzin  oleg korzhov  aleksandr shokhin  sergey rezontov  nelli galeeva  » more officers  directors mechel pao news briefrussias mechel may sell stake in coal project to investors from asia jun   update mechel to pay first full preferred share dividends since  jun   russias mechel says board recommends full dividend payment for  jun   briefdetsky mir europlan included to micex and rts indices as of june  jun   update mining group mechels net profit jumps on higher prices may   » more mtl news related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialssteel mechel pao adr nysemtl quotes  news  google financecookies help us deliver our services by using our services you agree to our use of cookieslearn moregot itmy accountsearchmapsyoutubeplaynewsgmaildrivecalendargoogletranslatephotosmoreshoppingwalletfinancedocsbooksbloggercontactshangoutskeepeven more from googlesign inhidden fieldssearch financeadobe flash player is required for interactive charts allowfinancemechel pao adrnysemtladd to portfoliocompanysummarynewsrelated companieshistorical pricesfinancialsmarketsnewsportfoliosstock screenergoogle domestic trendsrecent quotes  daysyou have no recent quoteschg   mechel pao adr  public nysemtl   watch this stock      jul   clo