nd various chemicals including benzene toluene solvent naphthalene ammonium sulphate resins and other products it supplies its products through its international sales network the company was founded in  and is headquartered in moscow russian federation with production assets in the united states and the russian federation mechel mining  mechel mining oao through its subsidiaries manufactures markets and exports metallurgical coals for steel companies in the russian federation and internationally it produces coking coal concentrates anthracites pci thermal coal iron ore concentrates coke and other coking and chemical products the company also manufactures coke gas and various chemicals including benzene toluene solvent naphthalene ammonium sulphate resins and other products it supplies its products through its international sales network the company was founded in  and is headquartered in moscow russian federation with production assets in the united states and the russian federation mechel mining oao operates as a subsidiary of mechel oao detailed description  krasnoarmeyskaya ulmoscow  russiafounded in  phone      fax      wwwmechelcomproductionmining key executives for mechel mining oao mr igor vladimirovich zyuzin chairman of the management board chief executive officer and director age  mr stanislav aleksandrovich ploshchenko chief financial officer and director age  mr benoit de meulemeester chief mktg officer and mgmt board member mr igor v khafizov chief executive officer of yakutugol holding company age  mr victor nikolaevich skulditskiy chief executive officer of southern kuzbass coal company age  compensation as of fiscal year  mechel mining oao key developments south kuzbass pao amends loan contract with mechelmining oao apr   south kuzbass pao signed an interestedparty deal an additional agreement to a loan contract with mechelmining oao the borrower the maturity is june   the deal value is rub  korshunovsky gok amends loan contract with mechelmining fe