 produces coke both for internal use and for third parties the power segment engages in the generation and sale of electricity and heat power mechel is headquartered in moscow expectations › mechel oao earnings whispers  earnings calendar monday july  before open  after close  tuesday july  before open  after close  wednesday july  before open  after close  thursday july  before open  after close  friday july  before open  after close  july  montuewedthufri august  montuewedthufri  show only confirmed earnings calendar for monday july   earnings whispers all earnings standard list view release time bmo amc all date confirmation confirmed not all earnings growth positive negative all sort az company time estimate whisper actual growth guidance sentiment volatility score surprise halliburton co hal  am et eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is hals stock going now downflatup hasbro inc has  am et eps rev   m  beatmeetmiss where is hass stock going now downflatup manpower inc man  am et eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is mans stock going now downflatup illinois tool works inc itw  am et eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is itws stock going now downflatup lennox international inc lii  am et eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is liis stock going now downflatup bank of hawaii corp boh  am et eps rev   m  beatmeetmiss where is bohs stock going now downflatup rpm international inc rpm  am et eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is rpms stock going now downflatup stanley black  decker swk  am et eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is swks stock going now downflatup arconic inc arnc bmo eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is arncs stock going now downflatup vf corp vfc  am et eps rev   b  beatmeetmiss where is vfcs stock going now downflatup petmed express inc pets  am et eps rev   m  beatmeetmiss where is petss stock going now downflatup scorpio bulkers inc salt  am et eps rev   m  beatmeetmiss where is salts stock going now downflatup opus bank opb  am et eps rev   m  beatmeetmiss where is opbs 